Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:22.56,Default,,0,0,12,,片名：野 战 排
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,天 那是我想的东西吗\N{\ren}Oh, man! Is that what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 新兵 欢迎来到越南 跟我来\N{\ren}All right, cheesedicks. Welcome to the Nam. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 是菜鸟\N{\ren}I'll be dipped in shit. New meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会很喜欢越南的 永远的\N{\ren}You dudes gonna love the Nam. For-fucking-ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,365天\N{\ren}365 and a wake-up. Oh, lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,10,,1967年9月B连第25队步兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:52.98,Default,,0,0,10,,在柬埔寨边境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,下面小心\N{\ren}Watch it below!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,莫尔豪 走快点\N{\ren}Morehouse, drop back to slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,查理 谁在队尾\N{\ren}Who's on tail-end Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,总部 这是六队 位置如下…\N{\ren}Eagle, Eagle, Ripper Six. Pos rep follows.;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,L A W A F…\N{\ren}Lemur, Alpha, Whiskey, Alpha, Foxtrot....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,华伦 你去队侧\N{\ren}Warren, you get out on flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,霍梅斯特 什么事\N{\ren}-Hey, Hoffmeister! -Yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你有香烟吗\N{\ren}You got a smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 没关系\N{\ren}-No, man, I don't. -Sin loi, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,B26 为何延迟了\N{\ren}Bravo 2-6. What's the delay on point?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,又找不到路了吗\N{\ren}Having compass trouble again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走\N{\ren}Get a move on, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在等什么\N{\ren}Boy, what you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会咬你\N{\ren}He ain't gonna bite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那是越南兵 死了\N{\ren}That's a good gook. Good and dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵 新兵\N{\ren}-Cherry. -Yo, cherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,行动 第六队说我们挡住了他们 完毕\N{\ren}Move it out. Six says we're jamming them up back there. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他去见鬼吧\N{\ren}Tell that dipshit to get fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是第25队 听好 我们很快便出发 完毕\N{\ren}This is 2-5. Be advised. We're moving out shortly. Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 你怎么了\N{\ren}What's the matter with you, Taylor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个大混蛋\N{\ren}You are one simple son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 对不起\N{\ren}I'm sorry, sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,叫另外那个新兵过来 嘉勒 还有军医\N{\ren}Get that other cherry up here. Gardner. And the doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 军医 上前来\N{\ren}Gardner, doc, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:07:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 军医 上前来\N{\ren}Gardner, doc, to the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 快过来 你他妈的\N{\ren}Gardner, get your ass up the hill, you fat fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大胖子 快点\N{\ren}Hurry up, bubble-butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有事 蚂蚁\N{\ren}-You all right? -Ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我脖子全都是蚂蚁\N{\ren}I got ants all over my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是红蚂蚁\N{\ren}You got some red ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,红蚂蚁是杀手 黑蚂蚁最可怕\N{\ren}Reds are killers. Black ants are the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 混球\N{\ren}Hurry up, lard-ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我很累\N{\ren}I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只喝一点\N{\ren}Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要喝太多 你不要再喝了\N{\ren}Don't drink too much. I don't want you drinking any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想你抽搐\N{\ren}I don't want you cramping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你带着太多东西\N{\ren}You're humping too much stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有一半是不需要的\N{\ren}You don't need half this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你拿\N{\ren}I'll haul it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但请你下次先向我请示\N{\ren}But next time check with me first, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 中士\N{\ren}Thanks, sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有事吧 没事\N{\ren}-Are you okay? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是总部 有直升机接近你们\N{\ren}2-2, this is six. I understand you have a bird inbound at your pos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,总部 请留意\N{\ren}Bravo Six, be advised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,军资直升机正驶来\N{\ren}Resupply helo is inbound at this time. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快点搬军火下来\N{\ren}Go, you people! Get that ammo off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个字不是这样写的\N{\ren}It ain't D-E-R-E. It's D-E-A-R.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且莎拉也不是那样写的 笨蛋\N{\ren}And Sarah ain't got no two R's, King. Damn, you dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 她会明白我的意思\N{\ren}Don't matter. She know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她也不大认识字\N{\ren}She don't read too good nohow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 又是猪肉\N{\ren}Look at this shit! Pork again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你换你的火鸡 我不能再吃这玩意了\N{\ren}Trade me that turkey loaf for this pork shit, man. I can't eat this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你抽了什么\N{\ren}What you been smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不用洗衣服 你要运动一下\N{\ren}I hope you don't get that laundry gig. Your ass need to hump, hump.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,白小子 你在等什么\N{\ren}Hey, white boy! What you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个洞不会自己出现的\N{\ren}That hole won't dig itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快点挖\N{\ren}Come on. Get your dick skin on that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,时间无多 快点挖…\N{\ren}You ain't got all day! Dig, dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有人写过 地狱是不可理喻的\N{\ren}Somebody once wrote, ""Hell is the impossibility of reason. ""
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方就像地狱\N{\ren}That"s what this place feels like.; hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来了一周 但已经讨厌这里\N{\ren}I hate it already, and it"s only been a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母 这一周很痛苦\N{\ren}Some goddamn week, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,最辛苦的事 就是这星期站岗三次\N{\ren}The hardest thing I"ve ever done is go on point three times this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我在做什么\N{\ren}I don"t know what I"m doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我连越共在我面前出现也不知道\N{\ren}A gook could be right in front of me and I wouldn"t know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在很累\N{\ren}I"m so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们早上五点起床…\N{\ren}We get up at 5.;00 a.m...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,整天走动 四五点钟扎营 挖壕沟 进食…\N{\ren}...hump all day, camp around 4 or 5, dig a foxhole, eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,然后整晚埋伏 或是当哨兵\N{\ren}... then put out an all-night ambush or a listening post.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是新来的 没有人教我任何事\N{\ren}Nobody tells me how to do anything because I"m new.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没人理会新兵 他们连你的名字也不想知道\N{\ren}Nobody cares about the new guys. They don"t want to know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵的生命不重要 因他没有经验\N{\ren}A new guy"s life isn"t worth much because he hasn"t put his time in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,若在越南战死 最好在最初几周\N{\ren}If you"re gonna get killed in Nam, it"s better to get it in the first weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,原因是你不会受太多苦\N{\ren}The logic being, you don"t suffer that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果幸运 留在外围防线…\N{\ren}If you"re lucky, you stay in the perimeter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫时能够睡三至四小时\N{\ren}... then pull a guard shift, so you sleep three or four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能真的入睡\N{\ren}But you don"t really sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我撑不到一年\N{\ren}I don"t think I can keep this up for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该来这里\N{\ren}I"ve made a big mistake coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有很多活动\N{\ren}We got beaucoup movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,第三部队在15公里外被袭击\N{\ren}3rd Battalion got hit 1 5 klicks north of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,越共在树上挂上地雷\N{\ren}Charlie had claymores strung in the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,整排军队被炸 真倒霉\N{\ren}Blew a whole fucking platoon to pieces. Bad shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,两个中尉和一个上尉被炸死\N{\ren}Got two lieutenants and a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\ren}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你想谁去埋伏\N{\ren}All right, who do you want on ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 你带你的小队出去\N{\ren}Elias, you take your squad out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,华伦 留下 我需要德斯和乔利亚\N{\ren}Warren, stay in, but I need Tex and Junior from your squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\ren}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,调动到20M的位置\N{\ren}Move out in 2-0 mikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为今晚轮到奥尼尔\N{\ren}I thought it was O'Neill's turn tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,特斯和莫尔豪经验不足\N{\ren}Tubbs and Morehouse are short.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,丰山明天放假 还要他们去吗\N{\ren}Fu Sheng is going on R and R tomorrow. You want to send them out on ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你要带新兵去\N{\ren}You got the fresh meat, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么都不懂 可能会遇到事情 仔细想想\N{\ren}They don't know shit and we'll probably run into something. Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 你想我怎样做\N{\ren}Great. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我为了一个混蛋要好好睡觉 而让手下被杀吗\N{\ren}Get one of my guys zapped so a lame ass can get his beauty sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尼尔…\N{\ren}Hey, O'Neill...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别再罗嗦\N{\ren}...take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用每天都这么讨厌\N{\ren}You needn't be a prick every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 叫手下准备好\N{\ren}Elias, get your men ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了三年 以为自己是耶稣\N{\ren}Guy's in 3 years, thinks he's Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尼尔 他们留下 但你要去\N{\ren}O'Neill, your short-timers stay in, but you go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要有经验的老兵\N{\ren}I need veterans out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩中士\N{\ren}Sergeant Barnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们面前应该由我下命令\N{\ren}I think in front of the men, I need to give the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\ren}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看来会下雨\N{\ren}Shit, looks like rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们整晚都要在雨中了\N{\ren}It's gonna piss on us all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,会令你脸烂掉\N{\ren}It'll put a serious case of crotch rot on that ugly face of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你为那个白人而冒险\N{\ren}Goddamn, man. You break your ass for the white man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是没有公义的\N{\ren}No justice around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尼尔又触怒中尉了吗\N{\ren}What's O'Neill got, a nose up the lieutenant's ass already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么总是我们负责埋伏呢\N{\ren}Why do we always get fucking ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是因为他们在玩政治\N{\ren}Because it's politics, man. Politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我有否给你看过露丝的照片 没有\N{\ren}-Did I show you a picture of Lucy Jean? -No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她会是我的另一半\N{\ren}She's the one for me all right, that Lucy Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她也在等我\N{\ren}She's waiting for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她很漂亮 你很幸福\N{\ren}She's real pretty. You're a Iucky guy, Gardner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你有你女朋友的照片吗\N{\ren}You got a picture of your girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们有一个被 留在家乡的可怜女孩 不是吗\N{\ren}That leaves some unIucky girl back home, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去\N{\ren}Tuck this in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,装进去\N{\ren}Shit-can this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要这个 转身\N{\ren}Don't need this. Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\ren}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯 跟乔利亚和泰勒一队\N{\ren}Tex! You got Junior and Taylor here on your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 不要乱来\N{\ren}Elias, don't mess with my pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚不是去喝酒 别烦我\N{\ren}I ain't getting greased tonight. Keep this cheesedick off my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你有泰勒\N{\ren}You got Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 你和我一组\N{\ren}Gardner, you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你迷路或和队友分开了\N{\ren}In case anything happens to you, you get lost or separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,千万不要大叫 知道吗 知道\N{\ren}-...don't yell out, okay? -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要到处走 我们会来找你 好\N{\ren}-Just sit tight and we'll get to you. -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,准备出发 小心谨慎\N{\ren}Saddle up! Lock and load!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,爸妈不想我来这里\N{\ren}Mom and Dad didn"t want me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想我以他们为榜样\N{\ren}They want me to be just like them.;
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,受人尊敬 工作勤劳 拥有家庭\N{\ren}Respectable, hard-working, a little house, a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母 他们快把我逼疯 你知道妈妈的\N{\ren}They drove me crazy with their goddamn world, Grandma. You know Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我一向都备受保护…\N{\ren}Having always been sheltered and special...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想像其他无名氏一样\N{\ren}...I want to be anonymous like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为国家效力\N{\ren}Do my share for my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就像祖父在一次大战时一样 和爸爸在二次大战时一样\N{\ren}Live up to what Grandpa did in the first war, Dad in the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在的确是无名氏了\N{\ren}Well, here I am. Anonymous, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,和没人在乎的一班人一起\N{\ren}With guys nobody really cares about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来自荒芜的地方\N{\ren}They come from the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没听过的小镇\N{\ren}Small towns you never heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,田纳西波兰斯基 密西西比布兰登\N{\ren}Polaski, Tennessee. Brandon, Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,犹他州波切本 宾夕凡尼亚的旺普\N{\ren}Pork Bend, Utah. Wampum, Pennsylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只念过两年高中\N{\ren}Two years high school"s about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,若他们幸运 会在工厂找到工作\N{\ren}If they"re lucky, a job waiting for them in a factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们大部分都一无所有\N{\ren}Most of them got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们穷苦而且不受欢迎\N{\ren}They"re poor and unwanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们却为我们的 社会和自由而战\N{\ren}...yet they"re fighting for our society and freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 他们知道自己是最底层的人\N{\ren}It"s weird. They"re the bottom of the barrel, and they know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们自称平凡人\N{\ren}Maybe that"s why they call themselves grunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因为平凡人什么都能承受\N{\ren}Because a grunt can take it, can take anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是我见过最有真本性的人 祖母\N{\ren}They"re the best I"ve ever seen, Grandma. The heart and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒\N{\ren}Hey, Taylor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵 轮到你\N{\ren}Hey, cheesedick, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 轮到你\N{\ren}-What? -You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定懂得用杀伤地雷吗 我肯定\N{\ren}-Sure you can work the claymores? -I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,拉下安全栓和撞击三次\N{\ren}Flick the safety off and bang on it three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,三次 我知道了\N{\ren}Three times. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要睡着 否则我不会放过你 知道吗\N{\ren}Don't catch any Z's on me, or I'll sling your sorry ass! Hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,知道\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我终于在泥泞里找到答案\N{\ren}Maybe I finally found it way down here in the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我可以从这里重新来过\N{\ren}Maybe from down here I can start up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我可以骄傲的做个 堂堂正正的虚假人\N{\ren}Be something I can be proud of without faking it. Be a fake human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我或许能看见我还没看到的东西 学一些我还没学到的东西\N{\ren}Maybe I can see something I don"t yet see, learn something I don"t yet know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你 很想你\N{\ren}I miss you. I miss you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉妈妈我想念她 柯里斯上\N{\ren}Tell Mom I miss her too. Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,乔利亚\N{\ren}Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 混蛋 轮到你\N{\ren}-All right, motherfucker. -It's your shift, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去\N{\ren}Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,引爆地雷\N{\ren}Blow the fucking claymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拉下安全栓\N{\ren}Take the safety off! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拉下安全栓\N{\ren}Take the safety off! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拉下安全栓 妈的\N{\ren}Get the safety off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,救我 乔利亚 到这里来救我\N{\ren}Feed me, Junior! Get over here and feed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天 冷静下来\N{\ren}-Jesus-fucking-Christ! -Easy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 嘉勒被打中 我快过来\N{\ren}-Doc, Gardner's hit! -Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我被击中\N{\ren}Oh, shit. I'm hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 泰勒被击中\N{\ren}Doc, Taylor's hit! Taylor's hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 军医\N{\ren}-Oh, shit. -Doc, doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,伤势怎么样\N{\ren}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有引爆地雷\N{\ren}He didn't blow his claymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,放松 只是擦伤 按着\N{\ren}Relax, man. It's a scratch. Hold this on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要骗我 伤势怎么样\N{\ren}Don't lie. How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他让他们进入 他当值时睡着\N{\ren}He let them walk right up on us! He was asleep on his shift!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\ren}No, I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大哈洛 留意着他\N{\ren}Big Harold, keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让他休克\N{\ren}Don't let him go into shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,住口\N{\ren}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,住口 忍住痛 忍住痛\N{\ren}Shut up and take the pain. Take the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,总部 这是六队 我们被袭击 完毕\N{\ren}Red rag, red rag, bravo six. I have NDPs at this time. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子 你会没事的\N{\ren}Hey, little guy, you're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心\N{\ren}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否知道你会不会死\N{\ren}Do you know if you're gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你感到一切都没事吗\N{\ren}Do you feel it'll all be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,胡说 你会离开这里\N{\ren}No morbid bullshit. You're about to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会给你一日三餐 白床单\N{\ren}They're gonna give you three hot meals a day. White sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的白人护士拿了你的钱 会给你性服务\N{\ren}Pretty white nurses will give you blow jobs if you pay them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过她 不要哄他\N{\ren}-I heard about them white bitches. -Don't baby talk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这个混蛋睡着了 他让他们进来\N{\ren}The cocksucker fell asleep. He let them walk right up on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,乔利亚 住口\N{\ren}Just shut up, Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,放松 好吗\N{\ren}You relax. Okay, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:23:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡不是…\N{\ren}It's not so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那么糟\N{\ren}...dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,多久\N{\ren}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,多久\N{\ren}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,直升机快来了 撑着点 你会支持着的\N{\ren}Bird's on the way. Hang in there. You'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 支持着 撑着点 你会没事的\N{\ren}Come on, Gardner, hang in there. You're gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.78,0:24:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 不要放弃\N{\ren}Come on. Don't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.68,0:24:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 嘉勒 不要放弃\N{\ren}Come on, Gardner, help me. Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.02,0:25:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好好看看这个狗屎\N{\ren}You all take a good look at this Iump of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.39,0:25:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要好好记住这样子\N{\ren}Remember what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.69,0:25:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们行差踏错…\N{\ren}You fuck up in a firefight and I guarantee you a trip out of the bush...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.36,0:25:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证你们不能活着离开\N{\ren}...in a body bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.53,0:25:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 混球 要提起精神\N{\ren}Out here, assholes, you keep your shit wired tight at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.74,0:25:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是 猪脑\N{\ren}That goes for you, shit-for-brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.38,0:25:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不能在埋伏时睡着\N{\ren}You don't sleep on no fucking ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.02,0:25:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,下次让我见到有人在埋伏时睡觉\N{\ren}The next son of a bitch I catch copping Z's in the bush...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.59,0:25:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定不会放过他\N{\ren}...I'm personally gonna make him suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.62,0:25:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是很认真的\N{\ren}I shit you not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.06,0:25:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,将他入袋\N{\ren}Tag him and bag him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.43,0:25:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有睡着\N{\ren}I didn't fall asleep, sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.24,0:25:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是乔利亚 住口 鸟大便\N{\ren}-It was Junior. -Shut up, chickenshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.50,0:26:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你有麻烦了\N{\ren}You're in big trouble, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.54,0:26:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,藉口像是屁眼 每个人都有一个\N{\ren}Excuses are like assholes. Everybody's got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.74,0:26:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别再胡闹\N{\ren}Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.55,0:26:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有两个队友需要照料\N{\ren}We got two men need attention here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.65,0:26:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾好军火和手榴弹\N{\ren}Police up your extra ammo and frags.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.42,0:26:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要留任何东西给越南人\N{\ren}Don't leave nothing for the dinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.69,0:26:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,背起嘉勒\N{\ren}Carry Gardner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.63,0:26:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,若有多几天去学习 他不会死的\N{\ren}Man would be alive if he had a few more days to learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.50,0:26:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒\N{\ren}Hey, Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.76,0:27:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\ren}What's in the breeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.97,0:27:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,三天轻松任务\N{\ren}Got light duty. Three days' worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.87,0:27:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜我们在基地营\N{\ren}No shit. Too bad we're in base camp anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.57,0:27:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿着什么 啤酒么\N{\ren}What you got? Beers?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.01,0:27:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,从长官那里拿的 他偷我们的物资\N{\ren}Stole some from the Top's supply. Shit, he's been stealing it from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.08,0:27:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了么\N{\ren}What are you, back?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.81,0:27:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是了\N{\ren}Yeah, it looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.38,0:27:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪里拿到的啤酒\N{\ren}Where'd you get the beers, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.42,0:27:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到的\N{\ren}I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.62,0:27:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,找到么 我会告发你\N{\ren}Found it? You're going on report, son, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.49,0:27:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们跟我来 有工作给你们\N{\ren}Both of you, come with me. I got a job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\ren}Motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.34,0:27:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不适合做这个\N{\ren}I'm too short for this shit, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.58,0:27:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们总是在玩弄我们\N{\ren}They're always fucking with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.78,0:27:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,从没有停止过\N{\ren}No letup.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.71,0:27:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是政治\N{\ren}Politics, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.75,0:27:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的政治\N{\ren}Fucking politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.55,0:27:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尼尔拍长官的马屁 拍的都快成马屁精了\N{\ren}That O'Neill's got his nose so far up Top's ass, he's gotta be Pinocchio.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.56,0:28:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,39天之后\N{\ren}Thirty-nine and a wake-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.23,0:28:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我就能离开这里\N{\ren}A pause for the cause and I'm a gone motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.43,0:28:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,回到现实世界 很好\N{\ren}-Back to the world. -I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.47,0:28:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我过了一百天\N{\ren}I broke a hundred the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.77,0:28:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还有92天 4月17日\N{\ren}Ninety-two left to go. April 1 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.94,0:28:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我便可以回加州了\N{\ren}Home to California.
