Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.01,0:45:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那一天我们都很敬爱他\N{\ren}That day, we loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.61,0:45:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那里\N{\ren}There he goes, sarge.
