Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.47,0:47:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,赶他们出来\N{\ren}Get them out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.51,0:47:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 这里有一个\N{\ren}Oh, fuck! We got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.71,0:47:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,赶他出来\N{\ren}Get the fuck out of the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.58,0:47:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,出来 混蛋\N{\ren}Get out of there. Come on, motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.28,0:47:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静下来 他们很害怕\N{\ren}Be cool! Be cool! They're scared, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.79,0:47:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们害怕吗 我又怎样呢\N{\ren}Oh, they're scared, huh? What about me, man?
