Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.79,0:48:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认为我们为谁而战\N{\ren}Who the fuck do they think we're fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.70,0:48:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个 你…\N{\ren}-You got one more! -Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.04,0:48:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么发现\N{\ren}Well, what have we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.28,0:48:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一 二 三 四支机关枪 捷克制米克58机关枪\N{\ren}They have one, two, three, four Mag 58 Czechoslovakian machine guns.
