Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.75,0:48:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有足够米粮供应一队军队\N{\ren}Barnes, they got enough rice here to feed a whole fucking regiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.59,0:48:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,华伦 带村长来\N{\ren}Sergeant Warren, you bring the honcho over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.10,0:48:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,特斯 出来 乔利亚 烧掉房子\N{\ren}Tubbs, get out of there! Junior, burn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.77,0:48:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 我不会伤害你\N{\ren}What the fuck's the matter? I wasn't gonna hurt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.87,0:48:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我看来想伤害你吗\N{\ren}Look like I was gonna hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.80,0:48:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不听我说 你为什么不他妈的听我说\N{\ren}Why didn't you listen to me?! Why didn't you fucking listen to me?!
