Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.98,0:48:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的过来 到这里 混球\N{\ren}Get the fuck up here! Come here, motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.11,0:48:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你在笑什么 你为什么不听我说\N{\ren}What are you smiling at?! Why the fuck didn't you listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.12,0:48:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死他们\N{\ren}Do them, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.72,0:49:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你在笑什么 想有点可笑的东西\N{\ren}What are you smiling at?! You want something to smile at, huh?!
