Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.90,0:49:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,跛子 跳舞吧\N{\ren}Dance, one-legger!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.50,0:49:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,跳舞…\N{\ren}Dance! Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.54,0:49:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,跳舞 跛子\N{\ren}Dance! One-legged motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.71,0:49:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\ren}Come on. Come on, let's go, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.65,0:49:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的 他在嘲笑你\N{\ren}Fucking pussy, man! He's laughing at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.76,0:49:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,越南人是那样笑的\N{\ren}That's the way the gook laughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.43,0:49:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\ren}Yeah, sure you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.13,0:49:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你很后悔吧\N{\ren}You're real sorry, ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.43,0:49:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你为曼尼他们的死感到内疚吧\N{\ren}You're just crying your little hearts out about Sandy and Sal and Manny.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.84,0:49:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,宾尼 算了吧 我们走\N{\ren}Forget about it, Bunny, huh? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.41,0:49:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你说呢\N{\ren}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.40,0:50:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 你看到他的头颅 是怎样爆开吗\N{\ren}Holy shit! You see that fucking head come apart, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.23,0:50:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过那样的脑袋\N{\ren}I never seen brains like that before, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.37,0:50:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌一定是她指挥一切的\N{\ren}I bet you the old bitch runs the whole fucking show.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.68,0:50:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是她割开曼尼的喉咙 她一定也想把我的睾丸割掉\N{\ren}She probably cut Manny's throat. Probably cut my balls off if she could.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.21,0:50:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,宾尼 离开吧 没有人看到什么\N{\ren}Bunny, we leave now, nobody saw a thing!
