Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.02,0:50:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死她吧 杀死整条村的人\N{\ren}Come on, let's fucking do her! Let's do the whole fucking village!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.16,0:50:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这个越南人头目脸上有些疤痕\N{\ren}There's scars on this gook honcho, sarge.
