Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.81,0:51:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他在轰炸中受伤 他一定是北越的人\N{\ren}-Says he was hit in a bombing raid. -He's a dink for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.69,0:51:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,问他这里为什么会有武器\N{\ren}Ask him why these weapons are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.73,0:51:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有选择 北越杀了抗命的老头目\N{\ren}They had no choice. The NVA killed the old honcho when he said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.43,0:51:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他说那些米是属于他们 莱纳 胡说\N{\ren}-He says all the rice is theirs. -Oh, bullshit, Lerner.
