Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.32,0:51:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道我在说什么吧\N{\ren}That cocksucker knows what I'm saying. Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.29,0:51:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定知道\N{\ren}Goddamn right he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.76,0:51:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他在说谎\N{\ren}He's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.00,0:51:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死他 看谁会说真话\N{\ren}Waste the fucker! Then see who talks.
