Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.15,0:53:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 我们还在等什么\N{\ren}Come on, sarge. What the fuck are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.35,0:53:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死他们 走开\N{\ren}-Let's do them! -Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.62,0:53:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他的女儿吧\N{\ren}This is his daughter, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.67,0:53:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你说谎 不 你说谎 你这个越共\N{\ren}You lie! No, you lie! You VC!
