Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.64,0:55:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不知道 我不知道你他妈的在说什么\N{\ren}No, I don't. I don't know what the fuck you're talking about, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.71,0:55:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快点出发 快 听到命令了吧\N{\ren}Move it out! Let's go! You heard the lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.55,0:55:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 走了 妈的 烧掉武器 然后离开\N{\ren}Taylor, let's go, for chrissake! Police up the weapons and let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.12,0:55:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哈洛 来吧\N{\ren}Come on, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.16,0:56:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,准备爆炸\N{\ren}Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.90,0:56:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,准备爆炸\N{\ren}Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.62,0:57:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\ren}Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.09,0:57:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 滚开\N{\ren}You fucker! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.99,0:57:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开…不要那样做\N{\ren}Get the fuck off! Don't do it! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.99,0:57:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 这是什么一回事\N{\ren}You fucker! What is this, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.67,0:57:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是同志吗\N{\ren}You a homosexual?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.03,0:57:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 她是越南人\N{\ren}What's your problem? She's a fucking dink.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.80,0:57:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她是人类 去你的\N{\ren}She's a fucking human being, man! Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.77,0:57:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 你这个可恶的新兵\N{\ren}Total fucking cherry, Taylor!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.14,0:57:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的禽兽 你们全部都是禽兽\N{\ren}Fucking animal! All of you! You're fucking animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.95,0:57:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\ren}Fucking lame fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.08,0:57:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你不属于越南 这里不适合你\N{\ren}You don't belong in the Nam. This ain't your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.05,0:57:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一点都不明白吧\N{\ren}You don't fucking get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.56,0:57:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不明白\N{\ren}You just don't fucking get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.66,0:57:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\ren}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.86,0:58:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,离开吧\N{\ren}Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.80,0:58:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,出发吧\N{\ren}Police up your dicks and let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.10,0:59:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都看不见 我看到\N{\ren}-I didn't see anything, sir. -I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.27,0:59:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩中士说那个是北越兵\N{\ren}Sergeant Barnes reported the dink as NVA.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.10,0:59:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的报告中 沃夫上尉是目击证人\N{\ren}My report will have Lieutenant Wolfe as being witness to the shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.07,0:59:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 好\N{\ren}All right, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.41,0:59:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩中士 是\N{\ren}-Staff Sergeant Barnes. -Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.11,0:59:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回到总部后我要详细报告\N{\ren}I want a full report from you when we get back to the CP.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.45,0:59:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你有日志 我有很多目击证人\N{\ren}You got a diary. I have plenty of eyewitnesses, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.78,0:59:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是现在\N{\ren}Not now, goddamn it! Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.39,0:59:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回到总部才调查这件事\N{\ren}We'll get into this at the base camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.72,0:59:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证如果发现非法杀戮…\N{\ren}I can promise you, if I find out there was an illegal killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.33,0:59:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会有军事法庭\N{\ren}...there will be a court-martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.36,0:59:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要全军作战 你们别再吵\N{\ren}Right now, I need every man in the field, and you two will cease fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.83,0:59:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩和伊利亚中士 听到吗\N{\ren}Staff Sergeant Barnes. Sergeant Elias. You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.24,0:59:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是 知道\N{\ren}-Yes, sir. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.44,0:59:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,明天你们从东面再去那越共地堡\N{\ren}We're going back into that NVA bunker tomorrow, this time from the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.94,0:59:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们休息一下 晚上七点钟回来开会\N{\ren}You people get some rest, and be back here at the CP at 1 900 for a briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.85,1:00:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是\N{\ren}-Yes, sir. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.19,1:00:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他们会在乎我们吗\N{\ren}Come on, man! You think these chucks give a fuck about you and me?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.43,1:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哈洛 也许会是你阻碍了巴恩\N{\ren}It could have been you, Harold, you got in Barnes' way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.30,1:00:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个宾尼呢\N{\ren}And that Bunny?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.33,1:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个疯子\N{\ren}That motherfucker's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.67,1:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他令我不寒而栗\N{\ren}I mean, he scares me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.84,1:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他很可怕\N{\ren}He just scares me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.14,1:00:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经受牵连\N{\ren}You bloods are getting too hung up on this shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.38,1:00:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这些越南人比你想像中聪明\N{\ren}These gooks are a lot smarter than you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.21,1:00:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩知道他在做什么\N{\ren}You know, Barnes knows his shit, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.48,1:00:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是北越兵\N{\ren}They was NVA, every last of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.19,1:00:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他带领我们走到这里了 他会带领我们走完这场战争\N{\ren}He got us this far. He'll get us the rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.29,1:00:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\ren}I don't know, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.12,1:00:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,基督教徒不会到处杀人\N{\ren}A Christian don't go around a village, cutting off heads and shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.23,1:00:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,情况失去控制了 完全失控了\N{\ren}This shit is really getting out of hand, blowing out of control.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.03,1:00:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你不知道怎样分别…\N{\ren}Seems to me that you don't seem to know the difference...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.20,1:00:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,事情的轻重\N{\ren}...the way you always shoot up that shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.50,1:00:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道…\N{\ren}I don't know, brothers...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.84,1:01:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但我内心大受伤害\N{\ren}...but I'm hurting real bad inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.75,1:01:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 伊利亚不能证明什么\N{\ren}Don't worry, sarge. Elias won't be able to prove a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.15,1:01:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个麻烦制造者\N{\ren}He's a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.45,1:01:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚像华盛顿的政客…\N{\ren}Elias is a water walker. Like them politicians in Washington...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.35,1:01:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,想独力打这场仗\N{\ren}...trying to fight this war with one hand tied around their balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.56,1:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有时间进行审讯\N{\ren}Ain't no need or time for a courtroom out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.03,1:01:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 谢谢你\N{\ren}-Sarge. -Thanks, Bun.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.73,1:01:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,情况怎么样\N{\ren}How did it go there, Bob?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.90,1:01:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个可恶的伊利亚\N{\ren}Yeah, thataway, sarge! Fucking Elias, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.74,1:01:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个卑鄙小人\N{\ren}He's a fucking rat, that's what he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.04,1:01:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他会连累这个连的所有人\N{\ren}He'll get everybody in this platoon in deep shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.28,1:01:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有人要教训他\N{\ren}Somebody ought to frag his ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.85,1:01:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为呢 会有调查吗\N{\ren}So, what do you think? Gonna be an investigation or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.95,1:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍布\N{\ren}Bob?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.36,1:01:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你太担心了 中士会解决他\N{\ren}O'Neill, you worry too much. Sarge will take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.63,1:02:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚天色很美\N{\ren}It's a beautiful night.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.37,1:02:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这里的夜晚\N{\ren}Yeah, I love this place at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.71,1:02:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,繁星…\N{\ren}The stars....
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.84,1:02:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,它们没有对与错 它们就是在那里\N{\ren}There's no right or wrong in them. They're just there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.72,1:02:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的比喻很好\N{\ren}That's a nice way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.66,1:02:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩憎恨你吧\N{\ren}Barnes has it in for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.16,1:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩相信他所做的一切\N{\ren}Barnes believes in what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.93,1:02:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 你相信吗\N{\ren}And you? Do you believe?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.60,1:02:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,1965年时吗 我会相信\N{\ren}In '65? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.11,1:02:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢\N{\ren}Now?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.04,1:02:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不相信\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.48,1:02:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,今天所发生的事只是开始\N{\ren}What happened today is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.68,1:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会输掉这场仗\N{\ren}We're gonna lose this war.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.29,1:02:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧\N{\ren}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.09,1:02:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的认为我们会输\N{\ren}You really think so? Us?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.66,1:02:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们欺负别人太久了\N{\ren}We've been kicking other people's asses for so long...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.66,1:03:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,现在轮到我们被打击\N{\ren}...I figure it's time we got ours kicked.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.64,1:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都在挣扎\N{\ren}Day by day, I struggle to maintain...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.28,1:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力维持体力和意志\N{\ren}...not only my strength, but my sanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.18,1:03:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很模糊\N{\ren}It"s all a blur.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.05,1:03:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有气力写信\N{\ren}I have no energy to write.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.45,1:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能分辨对与错\N{\ren}I don"t know what"s right or wrong anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.54,1:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的士气低落 出现内讧\N{\ren}The morale of the men is low. A civil war in the platoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.41,1:03:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一半支持伊利亚 一半支持巴恩\N{\ren}Half the men with Elias, half with Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.82,1:03:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多猜忌和憎恨\N{\ren}There"s a lot of suspicion and hate.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.32,1:03:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们竟然在自相残杀\N{\ren}I can"t believe we"re fighting each other instead of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.26,1:03:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,数着日子和留意着周围 没别的\N{\ren}Counting days and the six inches in front of my face. Not much else.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.40,1:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母 希望你一切安好\N{\ren}Hope things are well, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.70,1:03:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉妈妈和爸爸…\N{\ren}Tell Mom and Dad I--
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.00,1:03:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道告诉他们什么的 柯里斯上\N{\ren}Well, just tell them. Chris.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.86,1:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你以为会被派去洗衣服\N{\ren}Hey, big boy. I know you thought you had that laundry gig all laid out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.63,1:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把自己涂白 才能得到那些工作\N{\ren}Hell, I gotta paint myself white just to get one of those jobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.30,1:04:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我递了申请去割包皮 我要离开\N{\ren}Got my request in for a circumcision. I'm getting my big ass out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.57,1:04:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你会成为犹太教教士吗\N{\ren}What are you gonna do, become a rabbi?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.88,1:04:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,水蛭\N{\ren}Leech.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.58,1:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走\N{\ren}All right! Move it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.99,1:04:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不要喝 你会得痢疾的\N{\ren}Don't drink that, asshole. You're gonna get malaria.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.76,1:04:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望会\N{\ren}Yeah, I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.66,1:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\ren}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.87,1:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 莱纳被击中\N{\ren}Doc! Up here! Lerner's hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.24,1:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 华伦被击中\N{\ren}Sergeant, Warren's hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.88,1:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事 他们有火箭榴弹\N{\ren}-What's going on? -They got RPGs, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.08,1:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已在这里埋伏了很久\N{\ren}It's an ambush! They were just waiting for us here!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.08,1:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谁负责防守 莱纳和华伦\N{\ren}-Who's on point? -Lerner and Warren.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.39,1:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里\N{\ren}Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.79,1:05:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 混球 派火力上前\N{\ren}Goddamn it, you assholes! Get some firepower up there!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.86,1:05:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\ren}Right!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.34,1:06:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 火箭\N{\ren}Watch out! Rockets!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.38,1:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,莱纳在哪里\N{\ren}Where the fuck is Lerner?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.39,1:06:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他在木头那边\N{\ren}He's over there! By the log!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.24,1:06:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,开火坐标649602\N{\ren}Fire mission. Grid: 6-4-9-4-0-2.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.62,1:06:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,方向610\N{\ren}Direction: 6-1 -0--
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.05,1:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,调整发射 完毕\N{\ren}Adjust fire. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.72,1:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 他们会步步进逼\N{\ren}Lieutenant, they'll get in tight under the arty!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.06,1:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到缺口 让我带人去那边\N{\ren}I saw a cut. Let me take some men and roll up that flank.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.16,1:07:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,叫巴恩去 我们已有四个人受伤 你要我怎么办\N{\ren}Get Barnes! Elias, we got four down. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.07,1:07:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,红连在哪里 叫那些混蛋赶来\N{\ren}Where the fuck is Red Platoon?! Tell those assholes to get up here!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.87,1:07:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 你在这里做什么\N{\ren}Elias, what are you doing back here?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.38,1:07:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,第三连在这里 我们在这里\N{\ren}There's holes back here, 3rd Platoon's coming up here, we're here!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.95,1:07:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,若越军进入这些洞我们就要交锋\N{\ren}Dinks get in these holes, we'll be in a crossfire.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.25,1:07:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会互相开火 听来很不寻常\N{\ren}-We'll shoot each other. -Sounds far-out to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.49,1:07:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我在1966年的战役里见过\N{\ren}I've seen it happen. la Drang in '66.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.59,1:07:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会击溃我们 我需要三个人\N{\ren}They cut us to pieces. I need three men.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.39,1:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好 去吧\N{\ren}You got them! Take off!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.60,1:07:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,继续掩护我们\N{\ren}You keep pouring off that cover fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.47,1:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想在外面孤军作战\N{\ren}I don't want to be stuck out there with my ass hanging in the breeze.
