Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.06,1:36:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,先会发放烟雾 中尉和电讯兵已经死了\N{\ren}-Smoke will be first. -Lieutenant and radioman are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.53,1:36:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到地图\N{\ren}I can"t find the map.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.90,1:36:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们分布在四周 好几百个 我听到他们说越南话\N{\ren}They"re all around us. Hundreds of them. I can hear them talking gook.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.44,1:36:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,3A 看着烟雾 告诉我要转向哪里\N{\ren}3 Alpha, spot that smoke and tell me where to shift.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.51,1:36:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静下来 撑着点 我们会救你\N{\ren}Just calm down. Hang in there. We'll get you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.38,1:36:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里被袭 完毕\N{\ren}Where did the rounds hit? Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.70,1:37:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,3A6 你可以调整 开火位置吗 完毕\N{\ren}3 Alpha 6, how about those rounds? Can you adjust fire? Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.77,1:37:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,3A6 如果你不能说话 按键两次 完毕\N{\ren}3 Alpha 6, if you can't talk, just key your handset twice. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.26,1:37:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\ren}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.37,1:38:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,罗德里的坑被击中\N{\ren}Trip flare, Rodriguez's hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.05,1:38:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,火箭榴弹\N{\ren}RPG.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.49,1:38:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 法兰西 这里\N{\ren}-Taylor. Francis. -Over here, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.22,1:38:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事 罗德里的坑被炸\N{\ren}What's going on? Rodriguez's hole just got nailed.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.96,1:38:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 附近满布越南兵\N{\ren}Here it is. We got gooks in the fucking perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.86,1:38:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,完了…\N{\ren}Shit. That's it!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.06,1:38:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们打败了A连\N{\ren}They got through Alpha Company. Anything that don't identify itself...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.14,1:38:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,向任何不明物体开枪\N{\ren}...fucking blow it away.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.04,1:38:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 空军正在赶来 他们会拼命投弹的\N{\ren}Fuck. Air strikes coming in. They'll be laying snake and nape.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.24,1:38:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要离开散兵坑\N{\ren}Don't get out of your fucking holes. Stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.51,1:38:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\ren}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.68,1:38:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在侦察我们\N{\ren}They're probing us.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.99,1:39:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不惜一切地攻入\N{\ren}They'll go up and down, trying to get through.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.62,1:39:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,留在这里 冷静点 我很快回来\N{\ren}All right, stay here. Stay cool. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.79,1:39:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,F队 回音 威士忌 完毕\N{\ren}Foxtrot, Foxtrot. Echo. Whiskey. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.18,1:39:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁\N{\ren}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.72,1:39:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪\N{\ren}Don't shoot! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.59,1:39:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是埋伏 这边\N{\ren}It's the ambush. Over here, man, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.36,1:39:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 水\N{\ren}-Shit. -Water!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.83,1:39:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到处都是 正走向这里\N{\ren}They're all over the place! Hundreds of them! Moving this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.17,1:39:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们击溃我们 我们没有还击机会\N{\ren}They wiped us out! We didn't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.71,1:39:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,总部在哪里 后面\N{\ren}-Where's the CP? -Back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.64,1:40:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开 他们不会停止的\N{\ren}Get out of here! They're on my ass! They ain't stopping for shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.38,1:40:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 我们走吧\N{\ren}Hey, Taylor, let's di di.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.02,1:40:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你走\N{\ren}You go.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.56,1:40:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那边\N{\ren}There.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.50,1:40:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,停火…\N{\ren}No, hold it. Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.62,1:41:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开\N{\ren}Out of the hole! Fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.32,1:41:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快立刻壕沟 他们想炸掉兵坑\N{\ren}Get out of the foxhole! They're gonna blow it!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.29,1:41:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧…\N{\ren}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.49,1:41:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快点走 快 他们要炸掉…\N{\ren}Fuck's sake. Move your fucking ass! They're gonna blow--
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.75,1:41:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很可怕\N{\ren}Fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.02,1:41:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\ren}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.10,1:42:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 死吧\N{\ren}Die, you motherfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.88,1:42:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮\N{\ren}It's fucking beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.85,1:42:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么 你去哪里\N{\ren}What are you doing? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.90,1:42:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\ren}Come on, motherfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.80,1:42:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能做得更好\N{\ren}You can do better than that!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.27,1:42:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不断进攻\N{\ren}They just keep coming, man! Fuck this shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.61,1:42:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,回来 你这个懦夫\N{\ren}Get back here, you gutless shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.91,1:43:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,给我B连\N{\ren}Get me Bravo ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.24,1:43:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,C连报告三个坑失守 需要增援\N{\ren}Charlie Company reports hand-to-hand, three holes are down. They need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.18,1:43:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,立即派A连的两个小组前去 快\N{\ren}Okay, get two squads from Alpha down there right away. Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.71,1:43:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,空袭在哪里\N{\ren}Where's that goddamn air strike?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.95,1:44:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们去哪里\N{\ren}Hey, you two! Where the fuck are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.71,1:44:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,联络不到任何人吗\N{\ren}Can't you get anybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.07,1:44:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 联络不到巴恩他们\N{\ren}Negative contact. Can't raise Barnes, 2 Bravo, 2 Charlie, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.64,1:44:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,给我联络总部 总部\N{\ren}-Get me 6! -Bravo 6!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.78,1:44:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,柏加被击中 拉他进来\N{\ren}-Parker's hit! -Get him in!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.19,1:44:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们正在攻入\N{\ren}They're coming through our line!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.49,1:44:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩在哪里 他死了 他们全都死了\N{\ren}-Where's Barnes?! -He's dead! They're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.76,1:44:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,六队 中尉\N{\ren}Six, L.T.!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.66,1:44:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 我们被袭击 我们会撤退\N{\ren}Captain, we've been overrun. We're pulling back. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.13,1:44:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 撤退到哪里 到处都是他们\N{\ren}Goddamn it! Where will you pull back to? They're all over the perimeter!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.91,1:44:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你听着 你们要坚守作战\N{\ren}Now you be advised! You will hold in place and you will fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.21,1:45:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 即是指你 六队通话完毕\N{\ren}That means you, lieutenant. Bravo 6 out.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.04,1:45:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这里被袭\N{\ren}We got zips in the wire down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.41,1:45:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 B6 但我们不能再接近了\N{\ren}Roger that, Bravo 6. Can"t run it any closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.62,1:45:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备投弹 我们燃料充足\N{\ren}We"re packing snake and nape but we"re bingo on fuel.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.89,1:45:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的决定 投下所有炸弹\N{\ren}For the record, it's my call! Dump all you've got on my pos.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.69,1:45:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我再说投下所有炸弹\N{\ren}I say again, expend all remaining in my perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.43,1:45:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场很棒的战争 B6通话完毕\N{\ren}It's a lovely fucking war. Bravo 6 out.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.73,1:45:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 这是你的决定\N{\ren}Roger your last, Bravo 6. We copy it"s your call.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.17,1:46:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他们留守散兵坑 你们支持着\N{\ren}Get them in their holes. Hang tough, Bravo 6.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.44,1:46:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会从树顶投下炸弹\N{\ren}We are coming cocked for treetops.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.97,1:46:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩\N{\ren}Barnes!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.94,1:46:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\ren}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.12,1:49:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,给我找军医\N{\ren}Get me a medic.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.45,1:49:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快去\N{\ren}Go on, boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.94,1:49:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,下手吧\N{\ren}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.14,1:50:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 三点钟位置还有越兵活着\N{\ren}Look out, we got live gooks at 3:00.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.68,1:50:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\ren}Come on, Elmo! Move your flea-bitten ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.42,1:50:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\ren}You okay? You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.22,1:50:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你能走动吗\N{\ren}Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.19,1:50:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这里需要军医\N{\ren}Hey, doc! We need a medic up here!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.73,1:50:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 这里有伤兵\N{\ren}-Come on, Elmo. -Doc, we got wounded here!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.99,1:51:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,战争一定是很激烈\N{\ren}That must have been some fucking fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.82,1:51:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你一个吗\N{\ren}You alone here, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.46,1:51:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.49,1:51:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那些混球 他们留下我\N{\ren}Bunch of fucking faggots. They all left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.15,1:52:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,122个受伤 仍在点算中\N{\ren}1 22 wounded and still counting.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.12,1:52:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,估计有五百个伤者…\N{\ren}Estimate 500...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.55,1:52:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军22人阵亡 仍在点算中 完毕\N{\ren}...Victor Charlie K.I.A. 22 and still counting. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.26,1:52:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 是你吗\N{\ren}Taylor! That you?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.10,1:52:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,法兰西\N{\ren}Hey, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.30,1:52:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗 我还好 你好吗\N{\ren}-Hey, man, how you doing? -I'm okay. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.54,1:52:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好\N{\ren}Fine, man. Just fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.90,1:52:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们受过两次伤可以离开这里\N{\ren}Hey, dig it, we two-timers. We're gonna get out of here, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.47,1:52:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在医院再见\N{\ren}I'm gonna see you in the hospital. We gonna get high, high. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.72,1:52:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗 我没事\N{\ren}-How you doing? -I'm just fine, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.88,1:52:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好 因为第二连由你指挥\N{\ren}Good, because you got 2nd Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.49,1:52:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\ren}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.73,1:53:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好吗 准备好\N{\ren}-Ready? -You bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.86,1:54:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回想一切…\N{\ren}I think now, looking back...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.59,1:54:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是对抗敌人 而是自己\N{\ren}...we did not fight the enemy, we fought ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.66,1:54:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人就在我们心中\N{\ren}...and the enemy was in us.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.24,1:54:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,战争对我来说现在已经完结\N{\ren}The war is over for me now...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.60,1:54:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但它永远会存留在我的心中里\N{\ren}...but it will always be there the rest of my days.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.94,1:54:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚会和…\N{\ren}As I"m sure Elias will be...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.34,1:55:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩为了 像罗德所说的 “灵魂的掌控”继续作战\N{\ren}...fighting with Barnes for, what Rhah called, possession of my soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.25,1:55:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时会觉得…\N{\ren}There are times since...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.02,1:55:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是那两个父亲的儿子\N{\ren}...I have felt like the child born of those two fathers.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.63,1:55:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但无论如何…\N{\ren}But be that as it may...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.16,1:55:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有责任重建社会…\N{\ren}... those of us who did make it have an obligation to build again.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.53,1:55:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,教导别人我们认识的一切…\N{\ren}To teach to others what we know...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.07,1:55:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们利用剩下的一生…\N{\ren}...and to try with what"s left of our lives...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.01,1:55:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,尝试找寻生命的意义\N{\ren}... to find a goodness and meaning to this life.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.12,1:55:48.29,Default,,0,0,15,,献给在越战中牺牲的士兵

